---
import SiteHeader from "../components/SiteHeader.astro";
import SiteFooter from "../components/SiteFooter.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | DragonFruit"
  description="The short story behind DragonFruit, a workspace for people who think across fields and build with agents."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <main class="essay-shell about-main">
    <div class="about-copy">
      <div class="home-header about-topnav">
        <SiteHeader />
      </div>
      <h1 class="about-title">A personal letter from me.</h1>

      <section class="home-section home-intro about-story">
        <p>
          Hi, I&apos;m Miguel. I started DragonFruit from a feeling I couldn&apos;t ignore: modern work is scattered across too
          many rooms. Notes in one app, tasks in another, ideas in chat, and the real thinking lost between tabs.
        </p>
        <p>
          I wanted to build a workspace for people who move across disciplines, the same way I do. Designers who write.
          Engineers who research. Founders who need time to think before they decide. Small teams who want AI to help
          without creating more noise.
        </p>
        <p>
          So I shaped DragonFruit around one simple flow: a thought becomes a note, a note becomes a plan, a plan
          becomes a draft, and a draft becomes something real. Documents, tasks, and agents should live close enough to
          support that momentum, not interrupt it.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you&apos;re building across fields and trying to stay clear in the middle of complexity, this is for you.
          Thanks for being here.
        </p>
        <p>With love, Miguel.</p>
      </section>

      <SiteFooter />
    </div>

    <div class="about-illustration-wrap">
      <img
        class="about-illustration"
        src="/assets/about-dragon-renaissance-illustration.png"
        alt="Renaissance-style rose-ink engraving illustration of the DragonFruit dragon emblem"
        width="1555"
        height="1012"
      />
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
